---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms and Conditions | Your Service">
  <section class="bg-[#FAF8F5] text-[#3d1d0e] py-16 md:py-24 px-6 min-h-screen">
    
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl bg-white p-8 md:p-16 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
      
      <header class="border-b border-gray-100 pb-6 mb-10 flex flex-col gap-2">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black tracking-tight text-[#3d1d0e]">
          Terms & <span class="text-brand-blue">Conditions</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400 font-medium text-xs md:text-sm">
          Last updated: June 11, 2026 • Effective Date: Immediate
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-10 text-gray-600 font-medium text-base leading-relaxed">
        
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#3d1d0e] tracking-tight">
            1. Agreement to Terms
          </h2>
          <p>
            By accessing our website or utilizing the virtual assistant and corporate outsourcing services provided by <strong class="text-[#3d1d0e]">Your Service</strong>, you agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions. If you do not agree with any part of these legal boundaries, you are strictly prohibited from using our platform and must discontinue operations immediately.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#3d1d0e] tracking-tight">
            2. Intellectual Property Rights
          </h2>
          <p>
            Unless otherwise indicated, this website, including its source code, databases, operational functionality, software architecture, artwork, and graphics, is our proprietary property. However, <strong>all custom deliverables, structured reports, data configurations, and intellectual property explicitly developed by our assigned Virtual Assistants for your company belong entirely to you</strong> upon successful clearance of corresponding financial cycles.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#3d1d0e] tracking-tight">
            3. User Representations & Service Content
          </h2>
          <p>By registering an active service account or contracting talent, you represent and warrant that:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-6 flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm md:text-base">
            <li>All registration and corporate infrastructure information you submit is fully truthful, accurate, and current.</li>
            <li>You will maintain the strict confidentiality of your account credentials and system authentication keys.</li>
            <li>You will not utilize our remote staff or systems for any illegal, unauthorized, or unethical business workflows.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#3d1d0e] tracking-tight">
            4. Fees, Billing, and Payments
          </h2>
          <p>
            We manage our outsourcing solutions through structured monthly billings or custom task allocations. Detailed pricing rules are defined upon initial strategic onboarding. Late clearances or failed payment processing cycles may lead to immediate structural suspension of your assigned remote assistants until accounts are fully settled.
          </p>
          <div class="p-4 bg-brand-blue/5 border-l-4 border-brand-blue rounded-r-xl text-sm font-semibold text-brand-blue mt-2">
            Important Note: All dynamic scale configurations (upgrading or downscaling hours) require proper notice as outlined in your individual statement of work (SOW).
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#3d1d0e] tracking-tight">
            5. Term and Termination
          </h2>
          <p>
            These Terms and Conditions shall remain in full force and effect while you use our services. You may terminate your relationship with us following the operational notice periods stipulated in your active contract. We reserve the structural right to terminate service deployment or deny system access to any entity for breach of these agreements without prior liability.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#3d1d0e] tracking-tight">
            6. Limitation of Liability
          </h2>
          <p>
            In no event will <strong class="text-[#3d1d0e]">Your Service</strong>, its directors, remote specialists, or staff be liable to you or any third party for any indirect, consequential, exemplary, or incidental damages, including lost profit or data loss arising from your use of the platform or actions executed by matched talent outside our specified tracking frameworks.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 border-t border-gray-100 pt-8 mt-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#3d1d0e] tracking-tight">
            7. Governing Law
          </h2>
          <p>
            These conditions are governed by and construed in strict accordance with local corporate regulations and applicable international commerce frameworks, without regard to its conflict of law principles.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 border-t border-gray-100 pt-8">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#3d1d0e] tracking-tight">
            8. Inquiries and Legal Support
          </h2>
          <p>In order to resolve an operational complaint regarding service delivery or to receive further clarity regarding these boundaries, please contact us:</p>
          
          <div class="bg-[#FAF8F5] p-6 border border-gray-100 flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm font-bold text-[#3d1d0e] max-w-md mt-2">
            <span class="text-gray-400 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-xs">Legal & Compliance Department</span>
            <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-green"></span>
              Email: info@yourservice.com
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>